<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">亲爱的同学们：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">本学期的篇章即将落幕</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在你们收拾行李，准备回家的此刻</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">请记得把“安全”妥善收好带在身边</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">无论你正奔向家的方向</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">还是开启新的实践旅程</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">平安都是最坚实的守护</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">这个冬天</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">愿温暖与你同行</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">让安全守护每一段美好时光～</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Chapter.01 离校篇</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977542797.png" alt="1772977542797.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977542797.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>宿舍安全“三步曲”</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Step One</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>&nbsp;三关到位 不留隐患</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977638302.jpg" alt="1772977638302.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977638302.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>关水电</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：拔掉所有电器插头，关闭总电源，拧紧水龙头</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>关门窗</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：锁好门、关好窗，窗帘可适当拉上</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>关柜锁</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：贵重物品锁入柜中，钥匙随身携带</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"> &nbsp;临走前请化身“细节控”，把宿舍的水电开关挨个“点名”，不给安全隐患留一丝机会。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Step Two</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;六清到位 清爽过年</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977654066.png" alt="1772977654066.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977654066.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>清垃圾</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：带走所有垃圾，不留味道</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>清食品</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：处理开封零食，不给虫鼠“留年夜饭”</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>清床铺</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：整理被褥，盖上防尘罩</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">④</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>清桌面：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">物品归类收纳，桌面整洁如新</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">⑤</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>清地面：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">扫地拖地，让宿舍“深呼吸”</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">⑥</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>清水池</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：清洁洗漱台盆，倒掉积水，保持干燥卫生</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">切记千万不要与早春的回南天抗衡，不然你将喜提N份潮湿发霉套餐！离校时，只需要</span><span style="color: rgb(207, 19, 34); font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>紧闭门窗，在衣柜放上除湿盒、樟脑丸，将被褥、书本等易潮易发霉物品提前藏进防潮袋，</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">回南天和小虫子就无法拿捏你的宿舍宝贝们~</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Step Three</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;登记报备 安心离校</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977732515.jpg" alt="1772977732515.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977732515.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>整行装</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：📦 行李打包“断舍离”，贵重物品贴身带，电脑平板充电宝，钱包证件钥匙串，这些“保命神器”请锁进背包贴身放，别让它们在宿舍上演“消失的它”。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>填登记</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：如实填写离校去向，离校时间、回家路线、到家报平安，记得跟辅导员报备一声~</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>保联系：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">辅导员常联络，室友群内多沟通。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>重要提醒</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"> &nbsp;已返乡同学寒假期间不得擅自提前返校，如因特殊情况确需返校，须提前向辅导员和学院报备审批。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Chapter.03 &nbsp;返家篇</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977795952.png" alt="1772977795952.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977795952.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">回家安全“三预防”</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Chapter.01</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;🚗 出行路上“擦亮眼”，拒绝黑车和搭讪</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977824459.png" alt="1772977824459.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977824459.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>正规购票</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：通过12306、航空公司官网等正规渠道购票，不购买“黄牛票”。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>选择合规车辆</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：火车站、校门口人来人往，主动搭讪的“热心司机”、低价拼车的“神秘组织”，通通Say No！坐正规公交、打合规网约车，分享实时定位给家人，安全感直接拉满。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>遵守交规</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：遵守交通规则，不闯红灯、不翻越隔离栏。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">④</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>注意骑行安全</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：骑车时不看手机、不听音乐，不逆向行驶。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Chapter.02</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;💰 财产安全记心间，防盗意识不松懈</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977879620.png" alt="1772977879620.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977879620.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>贴身保管：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">贵重物品放在贴身口袋或包袋内侧，背包背在身前，时刻留意周围环境，候车候机时别只顾刷手机，背包要放在视线范围内，不给小偷“下手”的机会。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>分散存放：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">现金、银行卡、身份证等注意分开存放，不携带大量现金。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>警惕陌生人：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">不轻易接受陌生人提包、买票、照看东西等帮助。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Chapter.03</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;📱 人生安全防诈骗，守住钱包和信息</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977921267.png" alt="1772977921267.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977921267.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>保持警惕：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">不轻信陌生人搭讪，不随意透露个人信息，拒绝可疑链接和转账请求。“刷单返利”“中奖免单”“冒充客服退款”，这些套路别中招；陌生链接不点、陌生二维码不扫、个人信息不随意透露，反诈APP记得随时开！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>结伴而行</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：尽量结伴出行，独自出行要将行程告知家人，保持通讯畅通。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>紧急求助</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：遇到危险情况第一时间报警求助，并及时联系家长、辅导员，不盲目依靠自身解决问题。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>Chapter.04假期篇</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977964012.png" alt="1772977964012.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977964012.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>假期生活“五安全”</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>1. 居家安全</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;🏠 居家安全不马虎，防火防盗防意外</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977990919.png" alt="1772977990919.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772977990919.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>用电用气安全</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：不私拉乱接电线，不超负荷使用插座，使用燃气时保持通风，离开前关闭阀门；在家别乱拉电线，大功率电器别同时使用；出门探亲记得锁好家门，燃气阀门要随手关；</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>门窗安全</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：外出时锁好门窗，贵重物品妥善存放，不在家中存放大量现金</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>防火措施</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：不存放易燃易爆物品，熟悉消防设施及逃生通道位置，掌握基本使用方法。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>2. 饮食安全</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;🍜 饮食安全要注意，肠胃健康不添乱</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772978035694.png" alt="1772978035694.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772978035694.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>正规渠道：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">选择超市、正规农贸市场购买食品，注意查看生产日期及保质期，三无食品再馋也别买，守护“干饭魂”从管住嘴开始！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>生熟分开</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：生熟食品分开存放，防止交叉污染，加工前认真清洗食材，生冷食物要少吃。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>合理饮食：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">不暴饮暴食，少吃油腻辛辣食物，多食蔬菜水果，保持饮食均衡。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>3. 网络安全</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">💻 网络安全筑防线，文明上网不越界</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772978068534.jpg" alt="1772978068534.jpg" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772978068534.jpg" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>警惕诈骗：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">不轻信“中奖”“退款”“贷款”等电话短信，不点击不明链接，不扫描陌生二维码。警惕网络交友陷阱，不跟网友单独见面，虚拟世界也要保持清醒头脑。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>保护隐私</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：不在不可信网站填写个人敏感信息，谨慎添加陌生人为好友，不随意在陌生网站填写个人信息。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>合理上网</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：合理安排上网时间，不沉迷网络游戏，保持良好生活习惯。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">④</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>规范言行</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：不在网络散布谣言，不发表不当言论，自觉维护网络文明。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>4. 外出安全</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">&nbsp;🌍 外出游玩守规则，安全第一乐逍遥</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772978113771.png" alt="1772978113771.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772978113771.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>行程规划：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">外出前了解目的地天气、交通状况，避开恶劣天气出行。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>防患未然</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：出行请认准正规旅行社与景点，不擅自进入危险区域，从源头规避安全风险</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>保管财物：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在公共场所保管好手机、钱包等贵重物品，不显露贵重物品。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">④</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>遵守游玩规则：</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">去景区游玩要遵守秩序，不擅自前往未开发的野山、野水区域；遇到紧急情况别慌张，及时联系景区工作人员或报警求助。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>5. 实习安全</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">📝 社会实践多留心，保护自己放首位</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><img src="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772978172436.png" alt="1772978172436.png" data-href="https://jgfy.jxuspt.com/data/upload/editor/1772978172436.png" style="width: 50%;"></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">①</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>核实信息</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：参加实习、调研等社会实践时，要选择正规单位，签订明确的实习协议；不单独前往偏僻场所开展工作，遇到不合理要求及时向学校和家长反馈。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">②</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>拒绝收费</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：任何要求缴纳押金、保证金、培训费的行为都是骗局，正规企业不会收费。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">③</span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>保护权益</strong></span><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">：签订正规实习协议，明确工作内容、时间、待遇，遇到问题及时求助。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;"><strong>温馨提示</strong></span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">安全无小事</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">时时需警惕</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">希望同学们</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">在享受轻松愉快的寒假时</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">将平安牢记心间</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">让安全相伴左右</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">预祝大家度过</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center; line-height: 2;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 微软雅黑;">一个健康、充实、平安的假期～</span></p>